Pick up the blue pen to the right of the table.

Put the pen on the bottom shelf to the right of the chair.
Turn around and walk to the white table.
Pick up the blue pen.
Turn around and walk to the desk.
Put this pen on the other pen.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the bed, then turn left ad walk up to the white table, turn right and walk around to the end of the wooden table.
Pick up the closest blue pen off of the white table.
Turn left and walk towards the bed, then turn right and walk towards the door, turn left and walk over to the wooden desk.
Put the blue pen on the left side of the bottom shelf below the wooden desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the far right end of the white table.
